{
  "ADUs": {
    "ADU1": {
      "text": "I argue that there is an underappreciated respect in which the widespread availability of generative artificial intelligence (AI) models poses a threat to human connection.",
      "label": "claim"
    },
    "ADU2": {
      "text": "The central contention is that human creativity is especially capable of helping us connect to others in a valuable way, but the widespread availability of generative AI models reduces our incentives to engage in various sorts of creative work in the arts and sciences.",
      "label": "claim"
    },
    "ADU3": {
      "text": "Because relying on AI for certain generative tasks is less self-disclosive than the creative work such technologies supplant, this reliance threatens to weaken our connections to one another.",
      "label": "claim"
    },
    "ADU4": {
      "text": "Does the widespread availability of generative artificial intelligence (AI) models pose a threat to human creativity?",
      "label": "claim"
    },
    "ADU5": {
      "text": "If AI poses this sort of threat to human creativity, would that be a bad thing?",
      "label": "claim"
    },
    "ADU6": {
      "text": "My central contention is that, insofar as the widespread availability of AI models threatens human creativity, it threatens our ability to connect with other humans.",
      "label": "claim"
    },
    "ADU7": {
      "text": "Philosophers working on creativity have, by and large, overlooked the important role human creativity plays in enabling us to make valuable connections with each other.",
      "label": "premise"
    },
    "ADU8": {
      "text": "I argue that creative endeavors must be motivated by curiosity, and so they must disclose the creative agent’s inquisitive self.",
      "label": "premise"
    },
    "ADU9": {
      "text": "It is through self-disclosure, including the disclosure of the inquisitive self, that we put ourselves in a position to be seen by and connect with others through our creative pursuits.",
      "label": "premise"
    },
    "ADU10": {
      "text": "AI models can produce outputs that are valuable in many of the same ways that the products of genuine creativity are often valuable.",
      "label": "premise"
    },
    "ADU11": {
      "text": "Human creativity is often prized for its products. Among other things, our creative achievements have given us powerful art, successful scientific theories, and solutions to complex problems.",
      "label": "premise"
    },
    "ADU12": {
      "text": "If we come to rely on AI models instead of our own creativity, will anything of value be lost?",
      "label": "claim"
    },
    "ADU13": {
      "text": "I argue that one underappreciated value of creativity is that it plays an important role in connecting us to others, and I illustrate this with examples from both artistic creativity and scientific creativity.",
      "label": "claim"
    },
    "ADU14": {
      "text": "Creativity involves self-disclosure.",
      "label": "premise"
    },
    "ADU15": {
      "text": "Self-disclosure is essential for forming meaningful interpersonal relationships with others.",
      "label": "premise"
    },
    "ADU16": {
      "text": "Self-disclosure is also valuable for a general sense of connection we can experience even with people we do not know personally.",
      "label": "premise"
    },
    "ADU17": {
      "text": "Because creativity is driven by our curiosity, our creative pursuits demonstrate who we are as inquirers in an especially transparent way.",
      "label": "premise"
    },
    "ADU18": {
      "text": "Creative theorizing thus enables the sharing of ideas among scientists.",
      "label": "premise"
    },
    "ADU19": {
      "text": "The self-disclosure that occurs when we are creative makes it possible for others to understand us.",
      "label": "premise"
    },
    "ADU20": {
      "text": "This is essential for both our interpersonal relationships and a broader sense of human connection that includes the resonance of others’ art and the apprehension of others’ ideas.",
      "label": "premise"
    }
  },
